perl-file-basedir|-----handy-ruler------------------------------------------------------|
perl-file-basedir: perl-file-basedir (Use the freedesktop basedir spec)
perl-file-basedir:
perl-file-basedir: This module can be used to find directories and files as specified
perl-file-basedir: by the XDG Base Directory Specification. It takes care of defaults
perl-file-basedir: and uses File::Spec to make the output platform specific.
perl-file-basedir:
perl-file-basedir: http://search.cpan.org/dist/File-BaseDir/
perl-file-basedir:
perl-file-basedir:
perl-file-basedir: Packager: _PACKAGER on _BUILD_DATE
